    "breadcrumb": "About \u003e Outdoor Trip Reports",
    "content": "The Tahoe Ogul list is a list created by a now disbanded chapter of the Sierra Club, the Peak and Gorge Section. “Ogul” is the Washoe word for bighorn sheep.\nI started climbing this list (inadvertently) in 2015. I continued to slowly chip away until spring of 2023, when I set the goal of finishing the remaining 40 I had left before the end of July 2024. I managed to meet my goal, and had a great time doing so. The list got me out to amazing places I’d never have visited.\nMore information about the list can be found here\nOgul #63 - Raymond Peak Ogul #62 - Snow Valley Peak Ogul #61 - English Mountain Ogul #59 and #60 - Anderson Peak and Tinker Knob Ogul #58 - Mt Fillmore Ogul #57 - Haskell Peak Ogul #55 and 56 - Needle Peak and Lyon Peak Ogul #53 and 54 - Devil's Peak and Snow Mountain Ogul #52 - South Sister Ogul #51 - Mokelumne Peak Ogul #50 - Highland Peak Ogul #49 - Twin Peaks Ogul #48 - Phipp's Peak Ogul #47 - Ellis Peak Ogul #46 - Mt Elwell Ogul #45 - Hawkins Peak Ogul #44 - Mt Lola Ogul #43 - Mt Mildred Ogul #42 - Black Buttes Ogul #41 - Silver Peak - Southwest Summit Ogul #40 - Sierra Buttes Ogul #39 - Lookout Peak Ogul #38 - Reynolds Peak Ogul #36 and 37 - Genoa Peak and Duane Bliss Peak Ogul #34 and 35 - Da-Ek-Dow Go-Et and The Nipple Ogul #32 and #33 - Mt Patterson and Wheeler Peak Ogul #31 - Adams Peak Ogul #30 - Mt Rose Ogul #29 - Mt Siegel Ogul #28 - Desert Creek Peak Ogul #26 and #27 - East and Middle Sister Ogul #25 - Job's Peak Ogul #24 - Wade Benchmark Ogul #23 - Rubicon Peak",
